{
  "name": "RPlog_Atsvara_s_Hot_Takes",
  "title": "Atsvara's Hot Takes",
  "summary": "Aboard the Caspian battleship CMS Renaissance of Innovation, a celebratory reception follows the defenders' surprise victory in the first wargames exercise. Presav Crestian Tarasar quietly learns of a friend's death and shares the news, while his sharp-tongued young charge Atsvara deadpans a mock casualty report over a thrown donut that splatters the viewport. The flustered engineer Selko, struggling with her wardrobe, befriends Atsvara and is starstruck to meet the swoop racer and fighter commander Elana Tracer, who announces she is reopening the Marin Mountain resort. Over drinks, Tracer, Crestian, the Xi Charrian arms-designer ak, and Selko trade banter about the wargames, the new Baron and Hailfire battle droids debuting in the exercises, droid rights, and being underestimated. Tracer is called away by her comlink, and as the gathering winds down Crestian is summoned to meet with the Prelate.",
